== Requirements

* Rails 2+
* RubyGettext
* For Windows: Install poedit and add its bin directory to system path

== Installation

* Modify config/initializers/config.rb, config/database.yml
* Prepare DB
rake db:migrate
rake db:init
* Translate pofiles to mofiles
rake gettext:makemo

== Running

* Start web server
ruby script/server
* Start Fifo manager
ruby script/fifo_manager